{"tid":1556940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：羅范椒芬言論屬個人意見","createTime":"2019-09-10T02:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T03:28:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"36c3f446dea1b2b30429bdd0731fe23fa4b0d4fb","tid":1556940,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:28:16.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員羅范椒芬昨日在一個英文電台節目指稱，有少女為前線示威者提供「免費性服務」，行政長官林鄭月娥回應說，是她個人意見，又指近幾個月在社交網站有很多謠言，如果有人懷疑涉及不法行為，應向警方舉報，又指每個人都要消息的真確性都要極度小心，包括政府官員。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，如果有人想就傳言作出提醒或忠告，亦是可以理解。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，近來見到網上有很多假消息，令人信以為真，政府會盡最大努力予以澄清，但希望市民要理性、冷靜去看待相關消息，不要受謠言而產生錯誤的感覺。"},{"pid":"36b228034b78b96c0290dd059a2bee36c931bb90","tid":1556940,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1168023&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1168023%26csid%3D261_341&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=33fff26b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1168023&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"5cb4889bb5daf704cc421555e41e8023f5611f9e","tid":1556940,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"飯焦 : 痳病言論屬個人意見"},{"pid":"e62ff54cdd311f7fea92b5ac803bc79f873e0b58","tid":1556940,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cb4889bb5daf704cc421555e41e8023f5611f9e","tid":1556940,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"飯焦 : 痳病言論屬個人意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:32:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434